{"type": "article", "id": 29960, "title": "重新设计的经典座椅", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-21T23:01:35Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 22, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160721210029aMG167YyrBjtX4Nv.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>维也纳知名家具公司 Gebrüder Thonet 生产过不少经典的家具设计，其中大受欢迎的 No. 18 椅在 1859 至 1930 年之间就累计生产了五千万把。设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.i-n-d-j.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Atelier I-N-D-J</a> 最近就为这款拥有 150 年历史的经典产品进行了一番重新设计，将其命名为 <a href=\"http://design.i-n-d-j.com/PLUMP-THONET\" rel=\"nofollow\">Plump Thonet</a>。新款座椅增加了柔软舒适的黑色皮革坐垫，上面整齐排列了 16 个铜制圆孔以用来确定椅腿的位置，同时保留了经典造型的黑色椅背也由这些圆孔固定。一根纤细的铜制扶手从坐垫一侧延伸，穿过椅背连接起了两种不同的元素，带给人一种奇妙的视觉效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721210045xdqj2D7yEZS4IHt9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561458\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721210045KFlCrWgfInOT8JM9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607212100454ngv6cOlkYGWHxr7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721210045Zur7dbwESelkgF5N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.061458\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}